high_descs: Turn left to exit the room, turn left and walk straight to the counter with the sink.
Pick up the green dishsponge from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the bedroom on the left and reach the bed.
Put the dishsponge in the pan on the bed.
Pick up the pan with the scrub from the bed.
Turn around to exit the bedroom and turn left to the end of the passage and enter the room on the right to walk to the cabinet on the right.
Put the pan in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the DishSponge in the Pan and place it in the Cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left, leave the room through an exit in the upper left corner, then go to the far upper left corner of the hall where you reach a sink
Pick up a dishsponge from the sink.
Go back to the room you came from and approach the bed in the place where you can see a pan.
Put the dishsponge in the pan.
Pick up the pan from the bed.
Leave the room again the same way you entered, immediately turn left and head down the corridor in front of you all the way to the end, enter the room on the right, and get to the opposite corner.
Put the pan in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with the dishsponge in the cabinet.
